            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The worst school is Pathways Aravali; I learned nothing there. Its school imparts knowledge in subjects other than education. It instructs individuals on how to bully, manipulate, and fail in the real world. It continues to affect my mental health in the same way as any other institute. A company called Pathways Aravali specializes on manufacturing robots, not people. From the outside, it looks fantastic, but the more you discover about it, the more you fall into the abyss and are helpless to climb out. You suffer and sorrow from it for the rest of your life. Every choice you make in life starts the moment you step upon the school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
